text: Lim Geum-byeol (born 23 June 1998) is a South Korean taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in bantamweight at the 2015 World Taekwondo Championships in Chelyabinsk. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
